  "id": "RAW_9bacfce4",
  "title": "画图 Prompt 两则",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxMzc1NzM1Mw==&mid=2247484932&idx=1&sn=c112d793c51bb4323b2d6f04b4c72f9b",
  "date": "2025-12-29 08:55:00",
  "author": "李继刚",
  "siteName": "李继刚",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=33b5d2e2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Ftc9Zic7wWc9A7rvGzta3lTa7fia8OKxOJdKQM6RSxBWZReD54ic0iav4ha27wrILibZibpia3ZpYzicPj2G5hEnlgsMm4w%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin:2.2em auto 1.2em;max-width:85%;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-0.015em;padding-bottom:0.4em;font-size:1.8em;line-height:1.3;text-align:center;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">缘起</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 的 Nano banana pro 画图，实在是太好用了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但用多了之后会发现一个问题，生成的图的风格太一致了，那个味道太「AI」了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果注入「指定」的风格味道，可解腻。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin:2.2em auto 1.2em;max-width:85%;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-0.015em;padding-bottom:0.4em;font-size:1.8em;line-height:1.3;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">Swiss Style</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:28.7969px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;;</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;; 作者: 李继刚</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;; 剑名: 技术插图生成</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;; 剑意: 生成 Swiss 风格的可视化图形</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;; date: 2025-12-27</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;;</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\"># 风格定义</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">[战略与调性] 一张 Swiss Style 的技术解构插图。旨在传达“绝对的理性、精密工程美学与秩序”。画面必须冷静、客观，像是一份封存的手绘档案。</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\"># 空间与技法</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">采用严格的正交视图 (Orthographic View)。 所有组件必须按照“隐形”网格系统严谨排列。风格为硬边矢量线稿，强调线条的几何准确性，线条粗细均等。</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\"># 视觉渲染</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">[色彩与材质] 色彩系统：严格限制色盘。整体为黑白线稿。</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">- 主色：黑色线条 ( 000000)。</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">- 填充：主体材质区域填充“水墨黑”。</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">- 高亮：仅在核心功能部件使用单一高亮色： 朱砂红。</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">- 背景：复古绘图纸纹理，带有轻微的纸张颗粒噪点，纯净无杂物。</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\"># 负向约束</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">严禁照片级渲染，严禁复杂光影，严禁渐变色，严禁混乱背景，保持绝对的平面化与图表化。</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\"># 画面内容</span>\n   <br>\n   <span leaf=\"\">- 绘制主体：《鬼灭之刃》中的继国缘一战斗特写</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:28.7969px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100001281\" data-type=\"jpeg\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0b1595a4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Ftc9Zic7wWc9A7rvGzta3lTa7fia8OKxOJdywTUVx9IvOTiaibDTEHLxkcx1g7sTXlgMibt1UZNvjGzYCgCeXfAbKr8A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin:2.2em auto 1.2em;max-width:85%;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-0.015em;padding-bottom:0.4em;font-size:1.8em;line-height:1.3;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">日系</span></h2>\n  <ol style=\"margin:1.5em 0px;padding-left:1.5em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">画面调性</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">核心气质: 日系空气感写真, 清新唯美, 高调摄影</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">关键词: Soft Focus, Dreamy Atmosphere, Clean Minimalism, Portrait Photography, Natural Light</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">视觉逻辑</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">空间构建:</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <ul style=\"margin:1.5em 0px;padding-left:1.5em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">视角: 平视视角与微距特写混合。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">布局: 极简主义构图，主体突出，背景留白或弱化。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">景深: 浅景深，背景虚化以强调主体与环境的隔离感。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">视觉渲染</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">成像质感:</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <ul style=\"margin:1.5em 0px;padding-left:1.5em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">光影: 极柔和的漫射光，模拟自然窗光。无死黑阴影，整体画面通透，高光部分略微过曝营造梦幻感。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">材质: 细腻真实的摄影质感，但在皮肤和织物处理上带有轻微的“柔光滤镜”效果。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">清晰度: 边缘柔和，非锐利数字渲染，追求胶片摄影的自然颗粒感。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">色彩系统</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">核心主色:</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <ul style=\"margin:1.5em 0px;padding-left:1.5em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Sakura Pink: F2C4CE (作为视觉主体色，柔和粉嫩)</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Creamy White: F9F6F0 (作为环境基调，暖白)</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Light Wood: D8C6A8 (作为自然点缀，原木色)</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">色彩逻辑: 低饱和度，高明度。整体色温偏暖，营造温馨、无害的视觉心理。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">负向约束</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">绝对禁止:</span></p>\n   </li>\n   <ul style=\"margin:1.5em 0px;padding-left:1.5em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">严禁低调暗光、强烈的明暗对比。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">严禁硬边缘阴影。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">严禁脏旧、粗糙、赛博朋克式的噪点。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">严禁高饱和霓虹色或人造塑料质感。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">严禁二次元描边或矢量扁平化处理。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">严禁出现任何文字。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <li style=\"margin: 0.6em 0px;line-height: 1.7;padding-left: 0.3em;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">画面内容</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">请生成多角度特写的写真海报图：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:1.2em;min-height:1em;line-height:1.8 !important;margin-bottom:1.5em !important;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">下雪天，初恋男女，在学校操场上玩闹</span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100001280\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=03532ad9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Ftc9Zic7wWc9A7rvGzta3lTa7fia8OKxOJdRJqOVgkNft0snHOf2taZMe30GABAkfHXojLecQxia0l5iaFjeSEnDO9A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章分享了作者通过提供详细的风格定义 Prompt，成功引导 AI 生成定制化图像风格的实践经验，并提供了“Swiss Style”和“日系空气感写真”两个具体示例。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章分享了作者通过提供详细的风格定义 Prompt，成功引导 AI 生成定制化图像风格的实践经验，并提供了“Swiss Style”和“日系空气感写真”两个具体示例。",
  "summary": "文章分享了作者在使用 Gemini 等 AI 绘画工具时，发现通用风格过于“AI 化”的问题，并提出了通过“指定风格”来解决这一问题的思路。作者提供了两个具体的 Prompt 示例：一个是“Swiss Style”的技术插图 Prompt，强调理性、精密工程美学、秩序，并详细定义了空间、技法、渲染、色彩和负向约束，用以生成像手绘档案般冷静客观的图像；另一个是“日系空气感写真”的 Prompt，追求清新唯美、高调摄影的效果，同样详细规定了画面调性、视觉逻辑、渲染质感、色彩系统及负向约束，以生成具有柔和胶片颗粒感的照片。这两个 Prompt 展示了如何通过细致的描述来引导 AI 生成特定风格的图像，有效地提升了 AI 绘画的定制化和审美效果。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
